24:15.699 --> 24:17.666
because when my mother
sees a picture of my bride

24:17.700 --> 24:20.201
in that dress,
she's gonna be thrilled.

24:20.235 --> 24:23.270
Have you seen the dress?
Well, I didn't wanna see it
before the wedding.

24:23.305 --> 24:25.005
That's bad luck.
Yeah.

24:25.039 --> 24:28.540
Well, all I can say
is my mother really,
really loves you.

24:29.974 --> 24:31.975
Oh. Cindy.

24:32.010 --> 24:33.710
Nice to meet you.

24:33.744 --> 24:35.578
Uh, this isn't Cindy.

24:35.612 --> 24:38.247
This is Adrian
my daughter.

24:38.282 --> 24:40.715
Adrian, this is Fast Eddie.

24:42.284 --> 24:45.919
I'm sorry.
I meant, this is Judge Cooper.

24:45.954 --> 24:47.320
I'm a little nervous.

24:47.355 --> 24:50.389
They call me "Fast Eddie"
because I don't waste
any time in court.

24:50.424 --> 24:52.057
Oh, well, nice to meet you.

24:52.092 --> 24:53.559
It's nice to meet you,
too, Adrian.

24:53.593 --> 24:55.293
This is a special day
for your parents

24:55.328 --> 24:57.962
and, I understand,
a dream come true for you.

24:57.996 --> 24:59.597
Yeah.

24:59.631 --> 25:01.999
Something wrong, Adrian?
You feeling all right?

25:02.033 --> 25:03.967
You look a little pale.

25:04.001 --> 25:07.303
Okay, one, my fault
for not opening
the package sooner,

25:07.338 --> 25:09.005
and wearing
my sweats down here,

25:09.040 --> 25:11.408
thinking I was gonna
be putting on
this beautiful wedding dress.

25:11.442 --> 25:14.944
And two, certainly your mother
did not get married
in this dress.

25:14.978 --> 25:17.612
And three, she hates me,
because I was sitting
right next to you

25:17.646 --> 25:20.447
when you told her
I was a size two,
not a 32.

25:20.481 --> 25:23.649
I, uh,
don't know what to say.

25:23.684 --> 25:25.284
You look...

25:26.954 --> 25:28.221
funny.

25:28.255 --> 25:29.822
[laughing]

25:31.991 --> 25:34.359
I promise to never let this

25:34.394 --> 25:37.162
or anything else my mother does
come between the two of us.

25:37.196 --> 25:39.863
And I love you
for wearing that.

25:39.898 --> 25:41.932
I love you, Cindy.

25:43.100 --> 25:45.001
And I love you, too, Adrian.

25:45.036 --> 25:49.272
I only wish that I
had married your mother
when I should have.

25:50.374 --> 25:53.209
And I'm so glad
she had you.

25:53.243 --> 25:54.743
I am, too.

25:54.778 --> 25:56.979
I am, too.

25:57.013 --> 25:59.449
Okay, just do it.

25:59.483 --> 26:01.518
We'll need
a witness here.

26:06.893 --> 26:10.896
Dearly beloved,
we are gathered here today

26:10.931 --> 26:13.865
to join these two people
in holy matrimony.

26:18.654 --> 26:20.556
Oh, my God,
we're soaked.

26:25.490 --> 26:27.058
Here's the key.

26:27.092 --> 26:30.060
Let yourself in.
I'll go get the suitcase.

26:30.095 --> 26:31.795
Hi.

26:31.830 --> 26:34.064
- Hi, Ben.
- Hi.

26:34.098 --> 26:37.233
I guess the birthday party
got rained out. Hi, John.

26:37.267 --> 26:39.302
Say hi to Ben.

26:39.336 --> 26:42.037
Why don't I take him up
and get him changed?
No, I can do it.

26:42.072 --> 26:44.906
Or, yeah, I can go get
your suitcase or...

26:44.941 --> 26:47.542
You spending the night?
Hey, look who's here.

26:47.576 --> 26:49.644
The birthday boy.
Hi, Amy.

26:49.678 --> 26:51.445
You know Bunny?
This is our boss.

26:51.479 --> 26:54.414
We've never been introduced,
but I've heard a lot
of nice things about you.

26:54.448 --> 26:55.815
Same here.

26:58.618 --> 27:01.453
I took all
the party things upstairs,

27:01.487 --> 27:05.288
and Ben gave me some presents
from some of your friends
for the little guy.

27:05.322 --> 27:08.957
Yeah, I did. Of course,
I won't be coming to the party.

27:08.991 --> 27:11.392
No, 'cause you got
a big wedding
to go to tomorrow,

27:11.426 --> 27:13.760
and your dad needs you,
so why don't you take off?

27:13.795 --> 27:15.428
I can close up here.

27:15.463 --> 27:18.163
I didn't know
it was gonna be a sleepover
kind of birthday party.

27:18.197 --> 27:20.899
No wonder no one else
was invited.

27:26.371 --> 27:27.938
I don't believe that.

27:27.973 --> 27:30.207
Hey, hey.
You don't believe what?

27:30.241 --> 27:32.175
He was just complaining
this morning
that she makes him crazy.

27:32.209 --> 27:34.476
Now he's sleeping with her.
She's sleeping with him.

27:34.511 --> 27:37.045
You don't know that anyone's
sleeping with anyone.

27:37.079 --> 27:38.379
He just said,
"I'll go get your suitcase."

27:38.413 --> 27:40.781
None of your business, Ben.
Let it go.

27:40.816 --> 27:43.451
It is my business.
This is the family apartment.

27:43.485 --> 27:46.987
And it's--
it's completely wrong.

27:47.021 --> 27:49.889
It's okay, Ben.
It's gonna be fine.

27:49.923 --> 27:52.391
Go home,
take care of your dad,

27:52.426 --> 27:56.663
and do not,
under any circumstances,
ruin his wedding day.

27:56.698 --> 27:58.899
You hear me?
That should've been my baby.

27:58.933 --> 28:02.402
I would've been a good father.
I would've been a good husband
and a good father.

28:02.436 --> 28:04.870
Yes, you would, Ben,
but it's not your time.

28:04.904 --> 28:06.572
It's not your time.

28:06.606 --> 28:09.074
I'll see you tomorrow.

28:10.376 --> 28:12.043
[sighs]

28:15.114 --> 28:17.581
I'm sorry, Bunny.
I'm not angry at you.

28:17.615 --> 28:19.715
I'm angry with myself.

28:19.750 --> 28:22.852
I've completely ruined
my life.

28:24.455 --> 28:26.956
I hope not.

28:28.125 --> 28:29.458
[bell jingling]

28:30.660 --> 28:32.494
I'm not gonna do it tonight.

28:32.528 --> 28:34.195
We can't do it tonight.

28:34.229 --> 28:36.530
I'm not
emotionally prepared.

28:36.565 --> 28:38.131
And I wanna be wearing
my new dress,

28:38.166 --> 28:39.932
and I wanna have
my makeup done.

28:39.967 --> 28:41.901
I don't know.
Just, I don't
wanna do it tonight.

28:41.935 --> 28:43.635
All right.
I can wait one more night.

28:43.670 --> 28:45.437
Right.

28:45.471 --> 28:46.971
Are you nervous?

28:47.006 --> 28:48.706
No. I'm not nervous.
I'm ready.

28:48.741 --> 28:50.441
You're sure?
Yeah, I'm sure.

28:50.475 --> 28:52.342
Did you get the condoms?

28:52.376 --> 28:53.643
Yes.

28:53.677 --> 28:55.044
Can I see them?

28:55.078 --> 28:56.011
Uh, yeah.

29:03.319 --> 29:04.819
I've never seen one before.

29:04.853 --> 29:07.187
Well, we can look at one
together if you want,

29:07.222 --> 29:09.155
or I can just take care
of that myself tomorrow night,

29:09.189 --> 29:10.890
and you really don't
need to see it.

29:10.924 --> 29:13.326
Yeah, that'd be good.
I don't really wanna see it.

29:13.361 --> 29:14.795
All right.

29:14.829 --> 29:16.129
So what if it breaks?

29:16.164 --> 29:18.665
That would be bad.
You're not on the pill, are you?

29:18.699 --> 29:22.134
No. But as long
as it doesn't break,
we're okay, right?

29:22.168 --> 29:24.202
Right, but these things
can break.

29:24.236 --> 29:26.740
They usually don't.
It's never happened
to me before,

29:26.774 --> 29:30.376
but they can,
like with Adrian and Ben.

29:32.479 --> 29:33.946
What?
What?

29:33.980 --> 29:35.381
"With Adrian and Ben"?

29:35.415 --> 29:37.449
What are you talking about?
You said, "Adrian and Ben."

29:37.484 --> 29:39.451
Huh?
Yeah.

29:39.485 --> 29:41.119
Why would you say that?

29:41.153 --> 29:43.254
Why would you know that?
I mean, how would you know that?

29:43.289 --> 29:45.790
This isn't that "who, what,
when, where, and why"

29:45.824 --> 29:47.757
that they talk about
in journalism, is it?

29:47.792 --> 29:51.160
Hey, this isn't an interview.
No, it's off the record.
Now answer the question.

29:51.194 --> 29:53.962
All right, Madison.
This is what I was talking
to Grace about today--

29:53.996 --> 29:55.864
about Adrian and Ben.

29:55.898 --> 29:58.566
Oh, my God.
You cannot say a word--

29:58.601 --> 30:00.635
not a word-- to anyone.

30:00.669 --> 30:02.503
I'm serious.
She's pregnant.

30:02.537 --> 30:04.838
She doesn't know.
It's just that

30:04.872 --> 30:08.140
when something
like that happens,
it's pretty scary.

30:08.175 --> 30:11.377
But she told Grace because
she thinks she's pregnant,
and she wants an abortion.

30:11.411 --> 30:13.412
That's why Grace
told you.
Damn, you're good.

30:13.446 --> 30:16.314
Well, I'm not gonna
tell anybody. I promise.

30:16.349 --> 30:19.350
Please don't.
I'm sure the word
will get out soon enough.

30:19.384 --> 30:21.018
But Ben doesn't know.

30:21.052 --> 30:24.488
No one knows other than Grace
and you and me.

30:24.522 --> 30:27.424
That's it.
[sighs]

30:29.493 --> 30:31.127
Oh, God.

30:34.665 --> 30:35.631
[crying]

30:35.666 --> 30:37.466
[ringing]

30:37.500 --> 30:38.734
Hi, Grace.

30:38.768 --> 30:41.503
Hi, Adrian.
How are you?
How was the wedding?

30:41.538 --> 30:43.839
<i>Beautiful.
Really?</i>

30:43.873 --> 30:45.874
<i>That's nice.
Yeah.</i>

30:45.908 --> 30:48.643
Nice. They went away
for the weekend.

30:48.677 --> 30:51.778
Ruben surprised her
and got the bridal suite
at some Beverly Hills hotel.

30:51.812 --> 30:54.079
<i>Wow.
Yep. Wow.</i>

30:54.114 --> 30:56.481
<i>I have to go.
Wait.</i>

30:57.583 --> 30:58.950
Are you there by yourself?

30:58.984 --> 31:00.351
Yeah, I'm here by myself.

31:00.386 --> 31:02.019
Did you get
the early pregnancy test?

31:02.054 --> 31:04.488
Yeah. I bought one
on the way home.

31:04.522 --> 31:05.888
Do you want me to come over?

31:05.923 --> 31:08.390
No, Grace, I don't want you
to come over here.

31:08.424 --> 31:11.158
Adrian, I don't want you
to be alone
when you take the test.

31:11.192 --> 31:12.625
I'll come over.
I'm your friend.

31:12.660 --> 31:14.026
You know what, Grace?

31:14.060 --> 31:15.794
I don't know
if I want you to know.

31:15.829 --> 31:17.862
<i>Maybe you shouldn't know.
Why is that?</i>

31:17.896 --> 31:21.497
You know why, Grace.
And I saw you talking to Jack.

31:21.531 --> 31:24.899
If I find out I'm pregnant,
then it's my choice
as to what I do.

31:24.934 --> 31:27.401
It's not your choice,
and it's not Jack's choice.

31:27.436 --> 31:29.470
If you two ever get pregnant,
then it'll be your choice.

31:29.504 --> 31:32.372
Adrian, I just want you
to do the right thing.

31:32.407 --> 31:33.940
I will, Grace.

31:33.974 --> 31:36.776
I will do the right thing...
for me.

31:36.810 --> 31:38.544
<i>And the thing is, Grace,</i>

31:38.578 --> 31:40.945
I didn't get into this
all by myself,

31:40.980 --> 31:43.715
so I think the person
that I should have with me

31:43.749 --> 31:45.249
when I take this test
is Ben.

31:45.283 --> 31:47.317
<i>But don't say anything
to him.</i>

31:47.352 --> 31:49.886
<i>Let me be
the one to tell him.
I understand.</i>

31:49.921 --> 31:52.455
If you change your mind,
if you want me there,

31:52.490 --> 31:53.890
<i>just call me.
All right.</i>

31:53.924 --> 31:57.026
I will,
if I change my mind.

31:57.060 --> 31:59.494
I'm really sorry you're going
through all this, Adrian.

31:59.529 --> 32:02.163
Thanks, Grace.

32:02.197 --> 32:03.130
[beeps]

32:04.199 --> 32:05.366
[beeps]

32:06.668 --> 32:08.134
[sighs]

32:08.169 --> 32:10.236
<i>[recorded message]
It's me. It's Amy.</i>

32:10.270 --> 32:12.938
<i>Leave a message
for me and John.
[John laughing]</i>

32:12.973 --> 32:15.641
<i>[beeps]
Hi, Amy.</i>

32:15.675 --> 32:17.976
I'm really happy
I got your voice mail.

32:18.010 --> 32:20.011
I don't wanna bother you.

32:20.045 --> 32:23.681
I know that you and Ricky
are together tonight with John.

32:23.715 --> 32:27.017
But I just wanted to say

32:27.051 --> 32:30.853
that no matter what happens
between us in life, Amy,

32:30.887 --> 32:32.988
I'll always love you.

32:34.090 --> 32:37.058
And I just wanted you
to know that.

32:37.993 --> 32:40.695
And if you ever need me,

32:40.729 --> 32:43.163
you can call me,
and I'll be there.

32:44.632 --> 32:49.402
Good night, Amy.
And happy birthday, John.

32:56.882 --> 33:00.251
That was
a beautiful wedding.
Wasn't it?

33:05.285 --> 33:08.754
Ben, your dad and Betty--
they looked so happy
and so in love.

33:08.788 --> 33:11.256
Here's to love and happiness.

33:17.095 --> 33:19.896
Thank you
for last night.

33:19.931 --> 33:21.831
Thank you
for last year.

33:21.866 --> 33:23.933
You should really
thank your mother
for babysitting today,

33:23.967 --> 33:25.267
Robbie and John.

33:25.302 --> 33:27.903
She's used to
a lot of kids.

33:29.439 --> 33:32.608
- I love you, Hank.
- I love you, Alice.

33:32.642 --> 33:35.143
I wanna have
a wedding like this.

33:35.177 --> 33:39.046
- Anytime soon?
- Tenth grade's a little early.

33:39.080 --> 33:41.448
A little. Yeah.

33:51.358 --> 33:54.627
I just seems
more romantic to wait.

33:54.662 --> 33:57.130
You don't think Leo
and Betty waited, do you?

33:57.164 --> 33:58.965
I don't know.

33:58.999 --> 34:01.700
I doubt it.
But I get your point.

34:01.735 --> 34:03.802
I guess your mother
hates me now.

34:03.836 --> 34:05.837
Not just my mother,

34:05.871 --> 34:08.839
my father, my stepfather,
and my grandmother.

34:08.873 --> 34:11.040
Well, it's better
than doing it too soon.

34:11.074 --> 34:13.041
I'll win them over.
You'll see.

34:13.074 --> 34:15.975
I'm sure you will.
Yeah.

34:16.010 --> 34:17.744
So, is Kathleen
coming, George?

34:17.779 --> 34:20.947
I've always
wanted to meet her.
She was inside.

34:20.982 --> 34:22.349
I'll introduce you.

34:22.382 --> 34:24.050
You two have a lot
in common,

34:24.085 --> 34:26.252
what with being
newlyweds and all.

34:26.286 --> 34:27.719
Here you go, sweetheart.

34:27.754 --> 34:29.388
Oh, thank you,

34:29.422 --> 34:31.723
lover.
[chuckles]

34:31.757 --> 34:33.391
Oh, jeez.

34:33.425 --> 34:35.826
Hey, maybe you two would like
to be witnesseat our wedding.

34:35.860 --> 34:37.962
What wedding?

34:37.996 --> 34:39.630
Oh, there's Kathleen.

34:39.664 --> 34:41.364
Hi.
Where's your husband?

34:41.399 --> 34:42.998
He's delivering a baby.
Emergency.

34:43.033 --> 34:45.333
I did that one-handed.

34:45.367 --> 34:47.134
Hi, I'm Anne's mother.

34:47.168 --> 34:48.668
Sit down.

34:48.703 --> 34:51.204
I have so many
questions to ask.

34:51.237 --> 34:53.906
Yeah, join us.
This should be fun.

34:57.776 --> 34:58.843
Hi, Jack.

34:58.877 --> 35:01.145
Hey, Adrian.
How you doing?

35:03.181 --> 35:05.081
She told you,
didn't she?

35:05.116 --> 35:07.950
To be honest with you, yes.

35:07.985 --> 35:10.320
And you ld Madison?
No.

35:10.354 --> 35:12.322
All right.
Well, where is Madison?

35:55.925 --> 35:57.493
Ladies and gentlemen,

35:57.527 --> 36:00.795
I am proud to present
Mr. and Mrs. Leo Boykewich.

36:00.829 --> 36:01.929
[applause]

36:01.963 --> 36:03.964
The Sausage King
and his queen.

36:03.998 --> 36:05.832
[applauscontinues]

36:22.213 --> 36:25.381
Thank you for joining
Betty and Ben and me today

36:25.415 --> 36:27.382
to celebrate
our new lives together.

36:28.851 --> 36:32.887
I am truly a blessed man
to have Betty as my wife

36:32.921 --> 36:34.488
Ben as my son,

36:34.522 --> 36:38.057
and all of you
as our friends.
All of you.

36:38.091 --> 36:39.625
[crowd]
And to you.

36:39.659 --> 36:40.826
<i>Salud.</i>

36:40.860 --> 36:42.360
[Man] Cheers!
[Man #2]
You look beautiful, Betty.

36:45.330 --> 36:51.034
<i>Bunny.
<i>Oh, see?</i></i>

36:51.068 --> 36:53.603
My favorite song--
"Last Chance for Love."

36:53.637 --> 36:57.105
Do you get it?
I get it, honey.
I totally get it.

37:15.688 --> 37:19.090
<i>So, he's a gynecologist.</i>

37:19.124 --> 37:20.224
He is.

37:20.259 --> 37:21.892
So how long after a stroke

37:21.927 --> 37:25.329
is it safe to have sex?
Well, I'm not a doctor.

37:25.363 --> 37:27.130
But you've been married
to two of them.

37:27.164 --> 37:29.498
Yeah, well, you know,
I don't know about the sex,

37:29.533 --> 37:32.267
but alcohol is definitely
a no-no.

37:38.140 --> 37:40.508
<i>Who's that with Mimsy?</i>

37:40.542 --> 37:42.476
Well, if you'd been home
last night, you'd know.

37:42.510 --> 37:44.444
That's your new gramps.
Dad?

37:44.478 --> 37:46.145
That's right.
And if you were home last night,

37:46.179 --> 37:48.313
she wouldn't
have been home last night
alone with her boyfriend.

37:48.348 --> 37:50.281
I swear we weren't alone.
Griffin was there, too.

37:50.316 --> 37:53.417
We'll never know if that's true
or not, because you've
been known to lie.

37:53.452 --> 37:55.752
Ask Griffin.
Where is Griffin?

37:57.088 --> 37:58.555
Hey, Michael,
you're showing off.

37:58.589 --> 38:00.923
Hey, just because I dance
better than you do

38:00.958 --> 38:04.159
doesn't mean
I'm showing off.

38:04.193 --> 38:05.760
You're showing off.

38:05.795 --> 38:08.763
Oh, now look who's gone
and got all self-conscious.

38:08.797 --> 38:11.165
Oh, oh, yeah?
Oh, yeah?

38:15.870 --> 38:17.871
Come on. Let's dance.

38:17.905 --> 38:19.338
Oh, I can't.
I don't do disco.

38:19.373 --> 38:20.873
I still wanna talk to you

38:20.908 --> 38:23.075
right after I talk to him.

38:28.814 --> 38:31.616
You two better not have
done anything.

38:31.650 --> 38:33.818
I could say
the same to you, sister.

38:33.852 --> 38:36.653
<i>âª Come on, baby,
dance that dance âª
How'd it go?</i>

38:36.688 --> 38:40.323
That's for me to know
and you to find out,
for once.

38:40.357 --> 38:42.891
<i>All right.
âª Come on, baby âª</i>

38:42.926 --> 38:46.528
<i>âª Let's dance tonight âª</i>

38:46.563 --> 38:48.730
What'd you find out?
Not much.

38:48.765 --> 38:50.598
Ashley asked me about
birth control pills yesterday?

38:50.633 --> 38:52.867
What?
Yeah. I'll talk to her,
you talk to Amy.

38:52.901 --> 38:55.903
I talked to Amy.
We don't have to worry
about Amy and Ricky.

38:55.937 --> 38:58.238
We have to worry
about Amy and Ben.

38:58.272 --> 39:00.239
I thought--
Yeah, I did, too.

39:00.273 --> 39:02.775
What about Jimmy?
They're friends.

39:02.809 --> 39:04.843
Friends, just like us.
âª [big band, slow tempo]

39:04.877 --> 39:06.678
George, we are friends,

39:06.712 --> 39:10.247
and that's a good place to be
after all we've been through.

39:10.282 --> 39:11.849
I'm happy that we're friends.

39:11.883 --> 39:14.451
But I don't wanna get married
just because we had a baby.

39:14.485 --> 39:16.619
Three babies.
And two of them
are almost grown.

39:16.654 --> 39:19.021
One of them has
a baby of their own.

39:19.055 --> 39:21.656
We wouldn't tell Amy
to marry Ricky just because
they had a baby.

39:21.691 --> 39:25.693
I'm Ricky?
George, we've changed a lot
over the years,

39:25.727 --> 39:28.462
