other than the children,
we have that much in common.

39:28.496 --> 39:31.597
I mean, I love
a lot of things about you.

39:31.632 --> 39:34.199
I respect you.
I think you're funny.

39:34.234 --> 39:35.901
Thank you, finally.

39:35.935 --> 39:37.936
